patches.content:
QT += testlib widgets
TEMPLATE = app
CONFIG += console
CONFIG -= app_bundle
CONFIG += c++17

TARGET = test_diagram_items

SOURCES += tst_diagram_items.cpp \
    ../diagramitem.cpp \
    ../diagramtextitem.cpp

HEADERS += \
    ../diagramitem.h \
    ../diagramtextitem.h

INCLUDEPATH += ..

DEFINES += QT_DEPRECATED_WARNINGS

win32:CONFIG(release, debug|release): LIBS += -lQt5Test
else:win32:CONFIG(debug, debug|release): LIBS += -lQt5Testd
else:unix: LIBS += -lQt5Test

QT += testlib widgets
TEMPLATE = app
CONFIG += console

CONFIG += c++17

TARGET = test_commands

    ../deletecommand.h

INCLUDEPATH += ..

DEFINES += QT_DEPRECATED_WARNINGS

win32:CONFIG(release, debug|release): LIBS += -lQt5Test
else:win32:CONFIG(debug, debug|release): LIBS += -lQt5Testd
else:unix: LIBS += -lQt5Test

QT += testlib widgets
TEMPLATE = app
CONFIG += console

# Include source files for testing
SOURCES += \
    ../arrow.cpp \
    ../deletecommand.cpp \
    ../diagramitem.cpp \
    ../diagramitemgroup.cpp \
    ../diagrampath.cpp \
    ../diagramscene.cpp \
    ../diagramtextitem.cpp \
    ../findreplacedialog.cpp \
    ../mainwindow.cpp \
    ../main.cpp \
    tst_diagramitem.cpp

HEADERS += \
    ../arrow.h \
    ../deletecommand.h \
    ../diagramitem.h \
    ../diagramitemgroup.h \
    ../diagrampath.h \
    ../diagramscene.h \
    ../diagramtextitem.h \
    ../findreplacedialog.h \
    ../mainwindow.h

INCLUDEPATH += ..

# Test-specific configuration
DEFINES += QT_TESTLIB_LIB

# Output
TARGET = tst_diagramitem
DESTDIR = $$OUT_PWD
